"===[ Mappings ]========================================================

" Scroll up/down 20 lines at a time shift+j,shift+k
map <C-j> 20j
map <C-k> 20k

" Press 'shift+l' to go forward in history
map <S-l> :forward<CR>

" Press 'shift+r' to reload
map <S-r> :reload<CR>

" Press 'shift+j' to go to previous tab
map <S-j> :tabprevious<CR>
" Press 'shift+k' to go to next tab
map <S-k> :tabnext<CR>

" Press 'C-a' to select all
map <C-a> <C-v><C-a>

" Press 'C-c' to copy, 'C-v' or 'S-Insert' to paste, or 'C-x' to cut
map <C-c> <C-v><C-c>
map <C-v> <C-v><C-v>
map <C-x> <C-v><C-x>
cmap <C-c> <C-v><C-c>
cmap <C-v> <C-v><C-v>
cmap <S-Insert> <C-v><C-v>
cmap <C-x> <C-v><C-x>
imap <C-c> <C-v><C-c>
imap <C-v> <C-v><C-v>
imap <S-Insert> <C-v><C-v>
imap <C-x> <C-v><C-x>

"===[ fin ]=============================================================
